attributes.description: Agentcore memory dashboard showcasing memory operations performance and long-term processing analytics.

params.markdown:
# Memory

This dashboard provides insights into the following:
- Memory operation metrics, including event creation, retrieval, and listing across AgentCore Memory resources with invocation and latency tracking
- Long-term memory processing with extraction and consolidation operations broken down by strategy types and performance analysis
- Error monitoring and system health, including system errors, user errors, and throttling detection across all memory operations
- Strategy-based analytics showing extraction and consolidation performance by different strategy types with detailed latency and execution metrics

CreateEvent event creates an event in an AgentCore Memory resource. Events represent interactions or activities that occur within a session and are associated with specific actors.
